# 🔐 End-to-End Encrypted Chat Application

A real-time chat application built using **Node.js, Express, Socket.IO, TypeScript, MongoDB, and Libsodium**, featuring **End-to-End Encryption (E2EE)**, Email OTP authentication, JWT authorization, conversation history, and file sharing.

## Features

### Authentication

* Email OTP Verification
* JWT-based Authentication
* Dynamic User Registration
* Secure Login
* Protected API Routes

### Real-Time Messaging

* One-to-One Messaging
* Online/Offline Presence
* Typing Indicators
* Conversation History
* Unread Message Count
* Message Seen Status

### End-to-End Encryption

* Public/Private Key Generation using Libsodium
* X25519 Diffie-Hellman Key Exchange
* Shared Secret Derivation
* Client-side Encryption & Decryption
* Server stores only encrypted message content (ciphertext)
* Encrypted conversation history

### File Sharing

* Image Uploads
* File Attachments
* Secure attachment delivery

